'''''A Boy and a Girl''''' ([[Italian language|Italian]]: ''Un ragazzo e una ragazza'') is a [[List of Italian films of 1983|1983]] Italian [[romantic comedy film]] directed by [[Marco Risi]].<ref>{{cite book|last=Paolo Mereghetti|title=Il Mereghetti|publisher=B.C. Dalai Editore, 2010|isbn=88-6073-626-9}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last= Maria Pia Fusco |title= Il compito di noi trentenni <U+00E8> raccontare storie d' amore |newspaper=[[La Repubblica]]|date= 20 January 1984}}</ref> 

